# Smart AI Quiz Web Application

## Project Overview

Smart AI Quiz is a web-based quiz application that automatically generates quiz questions using Artificial Intelligence. The system allows users to log in, attempt quizzes, receive instant evaluation, and track their quiz performance through history records.

The goal of the project is to provide an interactive and intelligent platform for learning and testing knowledge in different subjects.

---

## Features

• User login system
• AI-generated quiz questions
• Topic selection for quizzes
• Timer-based quiz session
• Automatic answer evaluation
• Score generation after quiz submission
• Quiz history tracking
• Interactive and simple user interface

