## How to Run the Project

Step 1: Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/your-username/smart-ai-quiz.git

Step 2: Navigate to the project folder

cd smart-ai-quiz

Step 3: Run the backend server

python app.py

Step 4: Open the browser and visit

http://localhost:5000

---

## Application Workflow

1. User logs into the system
2. User selects a quiz topic
3. AI generates quiz questions
4. Quiz timer starts
5. User answers questions
6. User submits the quiz
7. System evaluates the answers
8. Score is generated
9. Results are stored in the database
10. Quiz history is updated and displayed

---

## Limitations

• Internet connection is required for AI question generation
